Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.80,0:00:08.52,flashback,Y. MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Look, Mother! I got a perfect score!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.80,0:00:14.03,flashback,YUMI,0,0,0,,You did great. That's very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:31.94,flashback italics,Y. MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:35.67,flashback italics,Y. MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,So that's not enough to satisfy her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.26,0:00:41.31,flashback italics,Y. MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I need to really excel if I want to \Nmake Mother truly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:47.31,flashback,YUMI,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:52.19,flashback,YUMI,0,0,0,,Please, just stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:01:01.76,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I dredged up some bad memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:05.46,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Okay, yeah, this is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:08.09,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I've caught a cold.
