Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:44.26,top,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:46.56,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:49.74,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Alya? U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:51.77,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Did Yuki tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:56.92,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yes. She asked me to bring you \Nsome medicine since you'd caught a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:58.69,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:02.20,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,That punk! Give me a little notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.62,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,May I come in for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:08.83,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh? You don't have to. \NJust the medicine is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:13.96,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yuki-san asked me to nurse you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:17.92,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Don't drag innocent strangers into your \Notaku fantasies, sister of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:19.92,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}Well, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.83,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,It was a false accusation, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:25.89,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.39,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.81,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,No need to be so wary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:33.86,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I-It's not like I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.86,0:03:36.40,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,It's just... This is all very new.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:41.03,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}And it smells of boy in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.66,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,That's not the kind of thing \Nyou want to say in a whisper!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:45.46,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Anyway, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:48.04,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What would you like? Porridge or borscht?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:49.86,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What's with the selection?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.38,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Hey, borscht is really good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:57.63,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,The veggies are boiled until tender, \Nso it goes down smoothly even when you're sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.63,0:04:01.30,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. I'll have the borscht, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:04.05,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Got it. Give me around four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:06.55,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nope, not waiting that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:11.08,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Using a pressure cooker would \Nspeed things up, but that's blasphemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:13.16,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Regular old porridge it is, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:16.33,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Very well. Let me use your kitchen.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.82,0:04:21.57,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Let's see... If I use pre-cooked rice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:21.57,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs10\c&H686D6C&\pos(194.908,24.182)\frx6\fry6\frz8.97}Search recipes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:21.57,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs13\c&H62666D&\frz7.962\pos(258.909,36.546)}Egg Porridge w/ Chicken Stock (using pre-cooked rice)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:21.57,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs11\c&H62666D&\frz9.791\pos(325.819,303.454)\frx2\fry0\clip(m 327 238 l 312 242 248 322 149 332 161 253 459 229 489 308 355 317 357 306 322 304 332 274 333 251)}Requires around 12 minutes. Approximately 230kcal (one portion).
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:25.45,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh, I have to heat it in the microwave, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.74,italics,ALYA,0,0,0,,He's using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:34.83,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, where was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:42.64,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun, your porridge is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:46.58,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:49.77,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,My deepest thanks for \Ngracing me with the apron look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:52.10,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I see you're doing better than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:53.96,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Think you can eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.35,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:56.66,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:57.90,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:02.61,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,This is yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.36,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:07.77,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:09.07,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Where are your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:13.23,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Dad's at work. No mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:16.25,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, we're a single-father home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.89,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:23.01,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Thank you. That was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:25.96,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,No problem. Did you take your medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:27.05,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:30.64,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go back to sleep. \NFeel free to leave whenever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:33.39,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,It's fine. I'll be studying in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:36.27,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Uh, you don't have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:39.35,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You're sick. Worry about yourself first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.54,0:05:42.04,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.04,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Damn, talk about oversleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:56.54,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Alya must've left by now, surely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:05.16,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Should you be up and about, Kuze-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:07.80,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,How are you feeling, Masachika-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:10.38,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Go ahead and lean on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:11.81,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:15.56,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,This looks like I'm pulling \Nmy maid into my arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:19.44,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Gotta be careful in this day and age. \NI might get canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:21.65,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.19,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Anyway, get away from him, Kimishima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:27.62,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,I will not. This is part of a maid's duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:31.20,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,But you're Yuki-san's maid, not Kuze-kun's.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:38.77,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Yuki-sama ordered me \Nto look after Masachika-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.77,0:06:40.71,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,As such, this falls under my duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:45.77,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,You can let me take over from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:49.13,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,It's getting quite late. Go home, Alisa-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:50.97,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hey! Phrasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:57.29,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Besides, shouldn't you be \Npreparing for tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:07:00.42,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Huh? What's tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:03.06,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Nothing. Just school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.75,0:07:04.72,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:11.21,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Take care of Kuze-kun, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:12.82,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Of course. You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:16.02,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,See you, Kuze-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.40,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:28.62,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Alisa-sama made borscht for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:29.34,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:30.93,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.18,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.38,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Let's dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.23,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:48.23,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Whew. That was amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.88,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Your medicine, Masachika-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:52.24,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:56.54,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Eating's made me sleepy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:59.24,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Will you be bathing tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:02.16,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hmm? I think I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:05.94,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Allow me to wipe you down, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:06.71,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:10.02,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll use a blindfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:12.43,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,How are you going to\Nwipe me down blindfolded?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.38,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,It's fine. Let me just go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:18.20,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,I'll sleep next to you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:19.74,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Chill!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:21.25,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,At least let me sing you a lullaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.39,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,No need for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.58,italics,AYANO,0,0,0,,Stare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.98,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord0\fnComic Sans MS\fs28\c&HB05C73&\move(169.455,235.091,176,235.091)}Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:28.38,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Ayano?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.92,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Yes? How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:33.20,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Go back to Yuki's and call it a night. \NThat's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.45,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.66,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:39.08,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.07,0:08:45.83,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I should've played that card right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.28,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.34,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Good morning, Masachika-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:08:59.85,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Seriously? I super overslept again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:02.76,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You skipped school for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:07.35,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Your health matters far more \Nthan some flimsy report card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:10.06,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:11.84,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,A lot better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.49,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:15.89,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,I'll prepare lunch right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:17.49,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Thanks. That'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:22.45,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:25.53,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Your appetite is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:29.25,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,However, you should \Ntake it easy today, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:31.47,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:33.51,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,School's done for the day, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.96,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Your medicine, Masachika-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:36.51,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:38.52,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Thank... you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:43.35,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hmm? Something's bothering me. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:46.23,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:51.24,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Ayano, let me see this medicine's package.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:53.93,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Ayano?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.24,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:03.14,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,This drug contains shit that'd \Nmake me sleepy, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:05.64,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,So it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:08.75,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Why didn't you warn me if you knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.84,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.93,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,I've committed a grave error \Nin offering you incompatible medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:19.26,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,You may discipline me in any way you see fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:23.42,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Was it Yuki who told Alya to get me this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.06,0:10:27.43,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I'm going to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:31.15,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,You should stay home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:32.19,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.25,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,However, I must say...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:35.13,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.54,0:10:38.70,Default,AYANO,0,0,0,,I believe it is too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.51,0:10:40.50,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:47.09,Default,BOY 1,0,0,0,,Our queen really is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.09,0:10:49.08,Default,BOY 2,0,0,0,,Yeah. Lady Alya did what she could,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:51.20,Default,BOY 2,0,0,0,,but she's a cut above.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.64,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Dammit! I was too complacent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:58.02,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I assumed she wouldn't try anything \Nuntil the closing ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:11:00.71,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I didn't expect her to make her move now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:05.97,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:08.48,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:11.44,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:14.63,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:17.65,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I messed it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.71,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I've wasted all your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.42,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:28.81,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,It started yesterday morning. \NYuki-san asked to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.87,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\bordo\b1\c&H151210&\frx14\fry54\frz337.1\fade(450,1)\pos(343,145)}Student Council Office
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:32.06,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Kuze-kun's down with a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:36.80,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Yes. Normally, I'd be the one \Nto go check on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:39.28,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,but I have something else to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:41.61,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Oh... Okay, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.61,0:11:43.14,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:47.18,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,In that case, here's the cold \Nmedicine he always takes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.83,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,and his address.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:50.32,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,If you would, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:53.19,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Got it. I'll drop by after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:57.25,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,There is one other thing I wanted to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.19,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:04.33,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Would you mind making a guest appearance \Non the lunchtime PA broadcast tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:05.20,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:09.86,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,I was thinking of covering \Nthe recent student congress tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.86,0:12:10.96,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Tomorrow...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:16.24,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Yes. It's a good opportunity to really \Ndrive home your victory in the debate, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:22.42,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I have no intention \Nof bringing that topic back up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:24.47,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.02,0:12:25.72,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:30.60,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Forget that part, then! \NWould you please appear anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:31.35,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:34.46,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,We can make our final \Nprogress report for the first term!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:35.73,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:39.17,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,O-Okay, that's more acceptable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:41.74,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Yes! Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:51.23,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,You two are truly set on not taking advantage \Nof that student congress victory, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.96,0:12:54.00,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,You figured it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:13:00.48,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,How could I not? I heard the recent \Nrumors about Nonoa-san's cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:03.26,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Just the fact that you're \Nletting it spread tells the whole story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:06.76,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Dearie me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.72,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Awfully laid-back, aren't you, Alisa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:13.82,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Are you even trying to beat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:15.15,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.49,0:13:27.40,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Do you not sense any danger at all \Nin waltzing into my territory?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:29.95,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,I must say, you're sorely lacking \Nin survival instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:33.04,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,You're such a sitting duck
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:37.03,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,that I just had to give you a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:39.79,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,There's more to the guest appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.33,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,You finally caught on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:47.60,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,It's happening right when Masachika-kun's \Nout sick. You should be more wary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.68,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,You're trying to take advantage?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:54.43,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Indeed. I wish to use this opportunity \Nto crash your stock as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:14:00.19,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,You think you can toy with me \Nas you please as long as I'm alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.56,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,You belittle me far too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:07.70,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Oh, feel free to run to\NMasachika-kun for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:13.83,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,No need. I will not be a burden to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:16.26,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Really, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:20.58,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Let me see what our ice princess \Ncan do tomorrow, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:24.82,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,I will not be beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:29.09,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I prepared for it as best I could, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:31.85,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,But then, after school ended today...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.43,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry, Alya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:38.47,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,What exactly are you apologizing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:43.18,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,I'm apologizing for the attitude \NI took with you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:50.33,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,I felt terrible about scheming \Nagainst a dear friend like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.00,0:14:56.62,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,So I took an overly aggressive stance \Nin order to force myself to go all-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:15:00.03,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,I'm fully aware of how \Nself-serving this may sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:04.44,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,but I do not wish \Nto sour our friendship, Alya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:09.84,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,I-It's fine. Raise your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:14.30,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,May I take that to mean \Nthat you accept my apology?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:18.64,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. It just goes to show \Nhow serious you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:23.15,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Thank you so much. I'm so glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:28.03,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,This may sound like an excuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:33.28,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,but there's a reason why I must \Nbecome president no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:34.41,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,What reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:38.04,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,I used to have an older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:42.75,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,He was far more talented than I could ever be,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:47.19,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,and our parents and grandfather \Nexpected great things from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.72,0:15:50.90,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,They were certain that he would take \Nthe Suou name to greater heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.12,0:15:54.67,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,But one day, he was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.74,0:16:01.57,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,I must live up to my family's hopes \Nin my brother's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:06.26,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,It is my duty to finish what he started.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:08.65,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.65,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:12.42,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:13.38,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:18.43,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,But, before that, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:19.16,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.47,0:16:23.25,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Why do you want to be \Nstudent council president?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:27.96,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Uh... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:30.26,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,It's time. Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.19,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,Good afternoon, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:37.77,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,This is Suou Yuki, \Nstudent council spokesperson,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:41.02,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,here to bring you another progress \Nreport on the student council's activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:44.47,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,We have a very special \Nguest joining us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:51.39,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Kujo Alisa here. \NThe student council treasurer...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:54.40,flashback,ALYA,0,0,0,,Er, it's my pleasure to be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:58.35,flashback,YUKI,0,0,0,,First-time nerves, I suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:04.04,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,It was the same after that. I was a total mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:06.09,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeesh, that's devious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:10.32,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,She acted like the bad guy to fire Alya up,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:12.60,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,only to bring out the sob story \Nbefore going live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:17.30,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,"I'm carrying the hopes of my entire family \Non my shoulders. How about you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:19.30,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm so mad at myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:24.36,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I was so easily shaken, \Nand I couldn't recover...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.95,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.95,0:17:32.52,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Your thoughts are spiraling in a bad direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:34.24,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:37.20,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I'm saying you're playing into Yuki's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:41.96,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Her goal wasn't to take the lead \Nusing today's broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:44.84,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Just think about it. \NWe only had school in the AM today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:47.47,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,There weren't many students \Nremaining in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:52.08,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,If she wanted to assert her dominance, \Nthere were better times to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:57.09,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You mean she was simply laying \Nthe groundwork for the closing ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:59.26,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:01.85,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,She just wanted to throw you off your game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:06.68,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I bet she was hoping to \Nleave you down in the dumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:09.46,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,And here you are, mad at yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.27,0:18:16.32,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Okay, I get it. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.81,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Why are you smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:21.57,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:25.33,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Wow, I am, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.54,0:18:30.33,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nah, just thinking she got us good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:35.34,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I don't really know why, \Nbut this is giving me goosebumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:42.22,sign_generic,SIGN,0,0,0,,{\pos(321,310.727)\bord1.4\3c&H202423&\c&HE5F0EB&}That look suits you too... I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:47.80,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I didn't have an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.80,0:18:48.92,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,To what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:54.73,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I couldn't answer her when she \Nasked me why I wanted to be president.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:19:01.24,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,She's going into the election \Nto win it for her family,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:05.08,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,but I'm only doing this for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:08.94,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,And I couldn't bring myself to tell her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.49,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed of myself for wavering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:19.12,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I hate that I couldn't answer her \Nwith my head held high!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:21.90,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Chin up, Alya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:27.39,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Your motivations aren't \Nas noble as Yuki's? So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:29.51,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Remember what I said before?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:33.27,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,You're a perfectly \Ncaptivating person as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:36.52,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I know fully well how driven
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.47,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,and how earnest and hardworking you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:41.35,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:44.51,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Keep your chin up. You're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:48.54,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Your charms do not pale in comparison \Nto Yuki's in any way whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:50.63,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,I promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:57.88,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,That sounded almost like you were \Nprofessing your love to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.33,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Shut it! I'm never doing\N that again, seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:03.38,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sheesh, I feel so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:05.72,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,My fever's coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:10.47,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Thank you. You helped me\Nregain my confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:13.52,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah? That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:17.50,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,You're right. There's no point \Ncomparing myself to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:18.58,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:23.72,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Even if Yuki-san's carrying on \Nher dead brother's spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:30.54,italics,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hey, sister of mine! \NYou made her think I'm dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:33.12,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,L-Listen, Alya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.67,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Heya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:38.22,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Wait, didn't you take the day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:39.67,Default,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:41.92,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Oh, I just got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.17,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.50,0:20:46.04,Default,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,Close your legs, Nonoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:50.35,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,What's the big deal? \NNot like anyone else is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:52.18,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:57.46,Default,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,I know this is belated, but Kuze-san, Kujo-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:21:00.65,Default,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,I apologize for my actions \Nand my appalling behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:03.59,Default,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:09.28,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,My bad, too. I should've stopped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:12.17,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Might be too late for that, \Nbut could you please forgive us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:15.62,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,That's for Alya to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:19.20,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,All I wanted was an apology \Nfor those insulting remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:23.30,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,As for you, Miyamae-san, \Nyou didn't even do anything to apologize for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:27.93,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,Uh, I think using plants \Ndefinitely merits an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:34.56,Default,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,Did you not bring up the congress \Non the broadcast to protect my reputation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:40.57,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,I didn't want to declare myself victorious \Nwhen I didn't defeat you in debate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:45.07,Default,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,I see. You're very prideful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:48.69,Default,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,But so am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:51.70,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Hold it, Taniyama. What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.27,0:21:56.96,Default,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,Facts are facts, my reputation be damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:22:01.34,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,So, what? You're gonna \Ngo declare your own defeat?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:04.84,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,With a PA broadcast? \NNo, at the closing ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:11.33,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Sorry, but as student council officers, \Nwe can't let you run wild at the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:16.73,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,If you want to repay Alya's goodwill in kind, \Ncould you do it another way?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:19.53,Default,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,What do you suggest?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.14,0:22:22.43,Default,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.43,0:22:23.11,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.64,0:22:27.79,Default,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,I'm not backing you two or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.79,0:22:31.65,Default,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,I still think you should go back \Nto Suou-san's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:32.71,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:35.87,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,But there's a reason I chose Alya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:37.98,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,And I bet you're starting to see it, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.39,0:22:43.75,Default,SAYAKA,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.04,0:22:46.46,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,No frickin' way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:50.97,Default,NONOA,0,0,0,,'Kay, count me in too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:53.47,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Thanks. Looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:22:56.65,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,See, Alya? This is what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:58.35,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Now we can beat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.67,0:23:01.81,Default,ALYA,0,0,0,,Huh? Beat them? \NI thought we were aiming for a draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:04.07,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,Nah, screw that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:06.65,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,They fired the first shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:09.46,Default,MASACHIKA,0,0,0,,So now we gotta destroy them.
